00:52:06.010 --> 00:52:09.150
In the context of one
type of meditation called

00:52:09.150 --> 00:52:11.220
the sevenfold cause
and effect meditation,

00:52:11.220 --> 00:52:14.570
we begin with recognizing
other living thins no matter

00:52:14.570 --> 00:52:20.254
who they are as one's closest
relation such as one's mother--

00:52:20.254 --> 00:52:22.720
and then thinking
about the kindness

00:52:22.720 --> 00:52:27.220
that we receive from the mother,
wishing to repay that kindness,

00:52:27.220 --> 00:52:29.635
developing loving kindness
and compassion passion,

00:52:29.635 --> 00:52:33.076
and then a sense of
universal responsibility

00:52:33.076 --> 00:52:35.200
