all living beings,

00:52:37.930 --> 00:52:42.340
and then finally that
conjoining of an understanding

00:52:42.340 --> 00:52:45.270
of ultimate truth, selflessness.

00:52:45.270 --> 00:52:48.890
All of this is
fundamentally centered

00:52:48.890 --> 00:52:51.430
around development of
love and compassion.

00:52:51.430 --> 00:52:54.530
